SUMMARY:South Meadow Blackberry Purge
DTSTAMP:20260323T153920Z
DTSTART:20260402T093000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Discovery Park. \\nHelp
	 us make way for more native plant habitat by removing the many invasive b
	lackberry plants encroaching on the south meadow. This will be a little bi
	t of cutting back the blackberry out of the forest edge of the meadow and 
	a bit of digging up roots. All tools will be provided. \\nRegister\n\nhttp
	s://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/south-meadow-blackberry-purge-15/
	\n\nFrom The Seattle Parks Foundation
