UID:jd-66WaiVLtlX01AnqBZg
SUMMARY:Beyond Mysticism Public Tour
DTSTAMP:20260323T153920Z
DTSTART:20260405T201500Z
DESCRIPTION:Revisit the Northwest Mystic artists from a fresh perspective o
	n a guided tour of Beyond Mysticism. From real places in Seattle like Pike
	 Place Market\, to abstract expressions of inner consciousness\, we'll div
	e into the art of both celebrated and underrecognized 20th-century Northwe
	st artists and their subjects. Led by a SAM docent\, explore the paintings
	 and sculptures that brought a rapidly changing Northwest region to life. 
	Tickets Free with admission\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/detai
